  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Push The Box 3D</strong> is a relaxing, isometric puzzle game where you move crates to clear your path and solve puzzles across beautifully designed 3D levels. Use crates to cross water, activate switches, and reach higher platforms, all while rotating the fully 3D camera to find the best angle for each challenge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Perfect for players of all ages, this no-fail puzzle game allows you to undo mistakes, ensuring a frustration-free experience. Every level has a unique layout, requiring clever thinking to use crates in creative ways. Elevators and buttons add extra layers of complexity as you navigate through different environments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once you've solved a level, compare your performance with others on the global leaderboard and see if you can complete it in fewer moves. Whether you're aiming for the top spot or just enjoying the peaceful puzzles, <strong>Push The Box 3D</strong> offers an engaging, light-hearted experience for puzzle lovers. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549620/extras/4f2a0be432b7e56ac04ee8fb886a814d.poster.avif?t=1727977553\" width=440 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549620/extras/4f2a0be432b7e56ac04ee8fb886a814d.webm?t=1727977553\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549620/extras/4f2a0be432b7e56ac04ee8fb886a814d.mp4?t=1727977553\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Use the block lift to go higher!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549620/extras/4890d4c4b6f3fd9b03c1fa4d788ed807.poster.avif?t=1727977553\" width=440 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549620/extras/4890d4c4b6f3fd9b03c1fa4d788ed807.webm?t=1727977553\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549620/extras/4890d4c4b6f3fd9b03c1fa4d788ed807.mp4?t=1727977553\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Push different kinds of blocks!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549620/extras/27e8b739f4cdae98fb2d0d97de0349f8.poster.avif?t=1727977553\" width=440 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549620/extras/27e8b739f4cdae98fb2d0d97de0349f8.webm?t=1727977553\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549620/extras/27e8b739f4cdae98fb2d0d97de0349f8.mp4?t=1727977553\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>. <br><strong>Activate triggers to your advantage!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features</strong>:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fully 3D environment with camera rotation</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Undo any mistakes, ensuring stress-free gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Crates serve as tools for navigating water, activating switches, and reaching higher platforms</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compare your performance on the leaderboard</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Easy-to-learn, relaxing gameplay with no time limits</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Test your strategic thinking and problem-solving skills in this family-friendly puzzle adventure. Can you master every level and push your way to the top of the leaderboard?</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Push The Box 3D</strong> is a relaxing, isometric puzzle game where you move crates to clear your path and solve puzzles across beautifully designed 3D levels. Use crates to cross water, activate switches, and reach higher platforms, all while rotating the fully 3D camera to find the best angle for each challenge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Perfect for players of all ages, this no-fail puzzle game allows you to undo mistakes, ensuring a frustration-free experience. Every level has a unique layout, requiring clever thinking to use crates in creative ways. Elevators and buttons add extra layers of complexity as you navigate through different environments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once you've solved a level, compare your performance with others on the global leaderboard and see if you can complete it in fewer moves. Whether you're aiming for the top spot or just enjoying the peaceful puzzles, <strong>Push The Box 3D</strong> offers an engaging, light-hearted experience for puzzle lovers. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549620/extras/4f2a0be432b7e56ac04ee8fb886a814d.poster.avif?t=1727977553\" width=440 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549620/extras/4f2a0be432b7e56ac04ee8fb886a814d.webm?t=1727977553\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549620/extras/4f2a0be432b7e56ac04ee8fb886a814d.mp4?t=1727977553\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Use the block lift to go higher!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_